# Auto deploy to teumu.online

When you finish meaningful code changes for this project (unless the user says not to deploy):

1. Commit and push to `origin main` on GitHub.
2. Deploy to production by running:
   `powershell -NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File deploy/push-and-deploy.ps1`
   from the project root (requires network + SSH).

Server: `root@160.30.4.98`, app dir `/var/www/iphone-store`, script `deploy/server-update.sh`.

If SSH fails with `Permission denied`, tell the user to run once on the server:
`bash deploy/install-deploy-key.sh`

Do not skip deploy silently — report push/deploy result to the user.
